Yes, I’m totally sunscreen-paglu 🤭and reapplying sunscreen in this summer heat is non-negotiable🥹
So honestly, this sunscreen spray is a solid 10/10 for me,except the nozzle. It’s not the best when it comes to spraying evenly on the face, and I really hope the brand considers upgrading the packaging next time. 🙏
Because formula-wise? Lightweight, mess-free, and super convenient,especially when you’re on the go!
Spray it on your face, body, anywhere,it’s genuinely made my reapplication game so much easier.
If they fix the spray part, it’s hands down a holy grail.

(Not sponsored. Just my honest thoughts. 💛)
